reviewText: listening to della reese is not to die for...it's to live for.

As much as I enjoy watching the Mambo King, this dvd has only 3 cuts of Tito, with some of the worst editing and camera work. The cameraman being out of focus, zooming in too quickly, bad editing swapping from camera to camera. This dvd is mostly Della and if I had to buy again, would not.
